*Video* kameru i kupio. (He bought a video camera.)
Učenici *vide*o lekciju u školi. (The students watched the lesson at school.)
Ona je *vide*la film preko interneta. (She watched the movie online.)
Oni *vide*u da je kuća za prodaju. (They saw that the house was for sale.)
Učitelj je *vide*o da je njegov učenik bio uspešan. (The teacher saw that his student was successful.)
Mi smo *vide*li vožnju u parku. (We saw the ride in the park.)
On je *vide*o snimak na televiziji. (He saw the recording on TV.)